snippet.title: Reel Steal - Nab appropriated art from evil billionaires!
snippet.description:
https://play.date/games/reel-steal/ Reel Steal is a heist game where a mysterious figure hires thieves to reclaim loot & justice. As renegades, nab appropriated art from evil billionaires, hurriedly making calling cards to leave in their place. The hook? You're armed only with a fishing pole.

➡️ More Playdate games https://itch.io/games/tag-playdate?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
